{"tid":2215920,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫委會6席位年底換屆 馬仲儀等3黃營醫生參選鬥撐警醫生","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"780b2b65db2bd5bd56c2175aef4e6ef670fa3863","tid":2215920,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:19.000Z","msg":"香港醫務委員會今年年底會就6個席位進行換屆選舉，當中3席由全體醫生選出。據悉，5人已報名競逐該3席，包括一向敢言的公共醫療醫生協會會長馬仲儀、前線醫生聯盟前副主席覃天笙及醫學會副會長鄭志文，3人會一起做競選工程。對手是去年曾聯署撐警的資深麻醉科專科醫生韋玉珍，以及執照醫生醫學會主席、外籍眼科專科醫生馬思特。有醫生表示，3名黃營醫生勝算較高，但醫委會委員有32人，即使黃營醫生佔據14席，親政府委員仍佔大多數；若政府趁社會動盪推行赤化醫生的政策，黃營要抵抗並不容易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LUOIG3VMBJH7JHGBNVGETJQV24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLUOIG3VMBJH7JHGBNVGETJQV24%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=b33f71de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FLUOIG3VMBJH7JHGBNVGETJQV24%2F&h=ae353fd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/LUOIG3VMBJH7JHGBNVGETJQV24/</a>"},{"pid":"71c3ebce5f376283e75da860b0a128d996a5d8c4","tid":2215920,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}